OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIncreasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with the chance of
OL,7,Fa few spots of light rain. Later in
OL,8,Fthe night, clearer spells develop,
OL,9,Faccompanied by freshening winds.
OL,10,FTurning cloudier again around morning
OL,11,Fwith some showery rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first, with
OL,14,Fpatchy light rain spreading southeast
OL,15,Fduring the morning. Then turning drier
OL,16,Fand brighter into the afternoon with
OL,17,Fjust the odd light shower. Fresh winds
OL,18,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
