OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain clearing Sunday morning,
OL,7,Fbright spells and scattered showers in
OL,8,Fafternoon. Dry start Monday, then
OL,9,Funsettled and changeable later Monday
OL,10,Fand Tuesday with rain or showers at
OL,11,Ftimes.
